history.content: There's just a delay in communicating between classes.berkeley.edu and the dept online schedule.

I want to take 294-129 next semester, as it's listed on the draft schedule here https://www2.eecs.berkeley.edu/Scheduling/CS/schedule-draft.html.

But it's not listed on the official class list here https://www2.eecs.berkeley.edu/Scheduling/CS/schedule-next.html; does this mean the class is not being offered?

It's also not listed on Prof. Canny's homepage, even though he is listed as teaching it under the draft schedule.
